snippet: The dialogue covers 54 minutes, from just before Malaysia Airlines Flight 370 left Kuala Lumpur to the last contact the pilots had with air traffic personnel.
abstract: Malaysian authorities release transcript of radio communications between cockpit of Malaysia Airlines Flight 370 and air traffic controllers before plane's disappearance; dialogue, which covers 54 minutes, provides no apparent indication of why plane veered from intended flight path.
lead_paragraph: The dialogue covers 54 minutes, from just before Malaysia Airlines Flight 370 left Kuala Lumpur to the last contact the pilots had with air traffic personnel.

headline.main: Transcript From Lost Jet Is Released By Malaysia
